<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7a278d72-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s7201"><num value="7201">§ 7201.</num><heading> Definitions</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In this chapter:</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I79" class="indent3 firstIndent-2" id="id7a278d73-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s7201/1"><num value="1" class="bold">(1)</num><heading class="bold"> Secretary</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1">The term “Secretary” means the Secretary of the Interior.</p>
</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I79" class="indent3 firstIndent-2" id="id7a278d74-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s7201/2"><num value="2" class="bold">(2)</num><heading class="bold"> System</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1">The term “system” means the National Landscape Conservation System established by <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s7202/a">section 7202(a) of this title</ref>.</p>
</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="id7a278d75-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/111/11/tII/s2001">Pub. L. 111–11, title II, § 2001</ref>, <date date="2009-03-30">Mar. 30, 2009</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/123/1094">123 Stat. 1094</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
